{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577690/extras/skill_animation_compilation_1_smaller_res.gif?t=1689442335\" /><br><br>&quot;Video Game Fables&quot; is a funny, lighthearted RPG adventure set in an abandoned game world that hasn't had a player in decades.<br><br>The world's script gets completely ruined by someone calling herself &quot;The Forsaken Princess.&quot; It's up to Aru (the world's princess), Nate (an NPC aspiring to be a hero), and Tator (the villain's son) to get things back to normal...or maybe change everything forever.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lighthearted humor throughout the dialog, characters, and world.<br></li><li>Fun narrative and story that doesn't rely on parody and has its own identity.<br></li><li>Challenging, fast-paced, turn-based battles that require strategy and quick thinking.<br></li><li>Twists on turn-based combat such as the CRIT system which lets you store a CRIT and use on a later turn.<br></li><li>Insane boss fights that break the battle system.<br></li><li>Unique XP and leveling system which lets you allocate resources to setup your party strategically.<br></li><li>Skill crafting, light class system that changes play styles slightly depending on equipped weapon, weapon upgrades, mining, fishing, simple gardening, and many more fun features.</li></ul><br><i>Original music by Levc EGM.</i><br><br><strong>See all reviews, podcast interviews, videos, publicity, buy merch, etc. on my website (click &quot;Visit the website&quot; on the right side of the Steam page).</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Topaz Crafter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577690/aab78b8bb061d5e67a1c4c7142b442f87796aa95.jpg"},{"name":"Sapphire Crafter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577690/7259ded36d0f5029f867908564a1a47ddc715a3d.jpg"},{"name":"Emerald Crafter","path":"h